    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scattering a substance in drops or particles on a surface often resulting in a surface covering of small specks, spots, or splotches.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
